replies.author: 神崎长闲
replies.txt_content:
本帖最后由 神崎长闲 于 2020-4-6 18:07 编辑 

直接定位错误信息：

[17:53:34] [main/WARN] [FML]: The coremod com.bioxx.tfc.TFCASMLoadingPlugin does not have a MCVersion annotation, it may cause issues with this version of Minecraft
[17:53:34] [main/WARN] [FML]: The coremod codechicken.nei.asm.NEICorePlugin does not have a MCVersion annotation, it may cause issues with this version of Minecraft

应该是模组的问题：
删掉模组打开游戏试试，如果可以打开，一点点排除模组，看看是谁的问题

replies.author: 倪灿nc
replies.txt_content: 你的显卡驱动确定一下

replies.author: ItIsEnderman
replies.txt_content:
安装CodeChickenCore（如果已安装，那就重装）
记住不要改名，任何Mod都不要轻易改名

https://www.curseforge.com/minec ... re/download/2262089

replies.author: 唯爱她°
replies.txt_content: 应该是某个mod的问题，hmcl不是有禁用功能 吗，先全禁用然后挨个放出来就好了！
